node.text:
Today we are thrilled to sit down with multi talented musician, father, and skateboarder Anthony Green aka @anthonygreen666 at his music studio in Doylestown, PA. You may have heard of Anthony through his work with bands like @circasurvive, @saosinofficial, #fuckinwhatever or just his solo Anthony Green moniker. What you might not have known is that Anthony shares a deep passion for skateboarding and music and is thankful for the lessons his kids learn through those shared arts. Anthony also discusses writing new music during the pandemic, why he works on so many different projects and how stoked he is to get back on the road. For any skateboarder, musician or parent this is a must see. We can’t wait to see you on the road, Anthony! Hit our @youtube channel to watch now!
🎥: @thekillatapes @trevarcushing
🎬: @richievaldez
#SantaCruzSkateboards

You definitely WON'T want to miss this one! Hit up our @youtube channel to watch now! 📡 Where should we roll in the next Screaming Vlog? Let us know in the comments!

Today we are hyped to sit down with @blakeular at El Sereno Skatepark for our latest installment of "What I'm Riding"! In this series we will be rapping out with your favorite members of the SC squad and dig in to their current setup to learn all about what is currently under their hood. What size board does Blake ride? How tight are his trucks? What is the sardine thing?! All of these questions and much much more are answered in Episode 4 filmed by @_nickhanson! Hit up our @youtube channel to watch now! Who should we tap for our next episode? Let us know in the comments!

8.375 in x 32 in Blake Johnson Beach Wolf 2 Pro Model Deck featuring Art by @tallboy666 
149 Standard Titanium @independenttrucks
